"Runner" = "Runner";
"Check status" = "检查状态";
"Model service" = "模型服务";
"Runner (WebDriverAgentRunner-Runner)" = "Runner（WebDriverAgentRunner-Runner）";
"Runner URL" = "Runner 连接地址";
"Runner is the WebDriverAgentRunner-Runner app on your iPhone. This URL connects the Console to Runner (port 8100).\n• On iPhone, use: http://127.0.0.1:8100\n• For LAN debugging, use the iPhone’s Wi‑Fi IP (make sure Runner’s Wireless Data is enabled)." = "Runner 是 iPhone 上的 WebDriverAgentRunner-Runner 应用（负责执行点击/滑动/截图等自动化）。本 App 通过这个地址连接 Runner（端口 8100）。\n• iPhone 上通常用：http://127.0.0.1:8100\n• 局域网调试可填 iPhone 的 Wi‑Fi IP";
"Service URL (Base URL, OpenAI-compatible)" = "服务地址（Base URL，OpenAI 兼容）";
"Required. Examples:\nDoubao: https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/responses\nOpenAI: https://api.openai.com/v1" = "必填。示例：\n豆包：https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/responses\nOpenAI：https://api.openai.com/v1";
"Required. Example: doubao-seed-1-8-251228" = "必填。示例：doubao-seed-1-8-251228";
"Required (unless already saved on device). Leave empty to keep the existing key." = "必填（若本机已保存过密钥，可留空继续使用）。";
"Doubao Seed: use Responses. Most OpenAI-compatible services: try Responses first; if unsupported, switch to Chat Completions." = "豆包 Seed：推荐用 Responses。大多数 OpenAI 兼容服务：先试 Responses；不支持再切到 Chat Completions。";
"Use Chat Completions when Responses is unsupported. More compatible, but usually uses more tokens." = "当服务不支持 Responses 时使用 Chat Completions。兼容性更好，但通常更耗 token。";
"Per-step max output (Token)" = "每步最大输出（Token）";
"Per-step output cap (Responses: max_output_tokens). Does not limit screenshot/input Token." = "限制单步输出长度（Responses：max_output_tokens）。不限制截图/输入 Token。";
"Per-step output cap (Chat Completions: max_completion_tokens). Does not limit screenshot/input Token." = "限制单步输出长度（Chat Completions：max_completion_tokens）。不限制截图/输入 Token。";

