"Advanced (optional)" = "高级（可选）";
"Reset" = "重置";
"Reset clears local runtime data (logs/chat/screenshots/Notes/token usage); Factory Reset also clears saved settings and the remembered API key; neither affects your model service." = "重置只会清理本机数据，不会影响你的模型服务。\n• 重置运行记录：清空日志/对话/截图/备注/Token 用量；保留已保存的配置。\n• 恢复默认设置：在上面基础上，还会清空已保存的配置（含 API 密钥、自定义系统提示词等）。";
"Reasoning effort (optional)" = "思考强度（可选）";
"Enable Session Cache (Doubao Seed)" = "启用会话缓存（豆包 Seed）";
"Responses only. Enables session caching for doubao-seed models to reduce tokens and improve stability." = "仅限 Responses API 模式。为 doubao-seed 模型启用会话缓存，以减少 token 用量并提升稳定性。";
"Half-resolution screenshots" = "截图分辨率减半";
"Shrinks screenshots by 50% before sending to the model, reducing Token usage and often speeding up responses." = "发送给模型前，将截图缩小到原来的 50%，减少 Token 用量并加快响应。";
"Use W3C actions for swipe" = "Swipe 使用 W3C actions";
"Recommended for games: makes swipe closer to a real finger gesture." = "推荐用于游戏：让 Swipe 更接近真实手指手势。";
"Annotate screenshots with actions" = "在截图上标注动作";
"Overlays click/swipe markers on per-step screenshots in Chat." = "在对话中的每步截图上标出点击/滑动等动作位置。";
"Debug raw conversation" = "调试：记录原始对话";
"Off by default. Stores per-step API request/response JSON with sensitive fields redacted (API key / Authorization / image base64)." = "默认关闭。记录每步 API 请求/响应 JSON，并对敏感字段脱敏（API key / Authorization / 图片 base64）。";
"Insecure TLS (model requests only)" = "不安全 TLS（仅模型请求）";
"Debug only. Skips certificate verification for model-service HTTPS requests and increases MITM risk." = "仅调试使用。跳过模型服务 HTTPS 证书校验，会增加中间人攻击风险。";

